Description: Jackson JS22 Dinky Electric GuitarIn my opinion, this guitar may be better than “new”. I purchased it for my son at a MegaStore and they pulled it from the warehouse and we unboxed it together (very cool store associate). It had never been played or displayed in the store ever. If you have been to a MegaStore on a weekend, you know how well played floor models get used and are still classified “new”. Only two players on this guitar - me and my boy (minus cool store associate). My boy later picked up one of my basses at home, and he hasn’t played guitar since. Any photo distortions on the back are the on the protective removable plastic coat. Believe the photos.
